    "method": "Claude Code research agent (general-purpose) — multi-network web crawl across Kwan Um Poland (zen.pl, kwanumeurope.org), Kanzeon Sangha (kanzeon.pl), Pusta Chmura / Sanbo (pustachmura.org), Kannon Polska (kannon.pl), Sangha Dogen Zenji / Kaisen (zazen.pl), Bodhidharma (buddyzmzen.pl), Polska Unia Buddyjska (polskauniabuddyjska.org.pl).",
    "coverageEstimate": "~60-70% of an estimated 35-50 active Zen practice places in Poland. Strong on Kwan Um network (largest in Poland), Kaisen Sōtō network, Kannon (Suzuki/Kwong), Kanzeon (White Plum), and Pusta Chmura (Sanbō Zen). Weaker on small Plum Village lay sanghas and informal Bodhidharma branches.",
    "knownGaps": [
      "Polski Związek Buddyjski Zen Soto (polskizenso.pl) was unreachable (ECONNREFUSED) — Sōtō Sotoshu-affiliated groups outside Kaisen network underrepresented.",
      "Sanbo Zen Polska does not maintain a public directory; only Pusta Chmura (Willigis Jäger / Sanbō-Kyōdan offshoot) cities captured.",
      "Plum Village lay sanghas (Sangha Uśmiech Buddy Warsaw, Sangha Cud Uważności Wrocław) — partial; full national Plum Village directory not exhaustively scraped.",
      "Bodhidharma association has 2 centers per public registry but only Falenica address is publicly listed; second center not enumerated.",
      "Mu Sang Sa Polska / Korean Zen monastery in Wisła Cieńków under construction at time of collection."
    ]
